  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Eiger is on a half board basis.</p>
<p>Each morning you can enjoy a varied buffet breakfast with classis continental offerings and additional hot options. Please note for early departures a packed breakfast can be arranged through reception.</p>
<p>When you return from a day on the slopes, enjoy a four course evening meal with a choice of main course. </p>
<p>For children under the age of three, meals are payable locally.</p>
<p>Christmas and New Year dinners are included</p>]]></cateringDescription>
