  <description><![CDATA[<p>Run by the charming Stähli family who make all guests very welcome, the Eiger is a popular hotel with good facilities and superb mountain views. The skiing is easily accessed either by the little mountain railway just opposite, the Allmendhubel funicular 500 metres away, or the Schilthorn cable-car 800 metres away. </p>
<h2>Incredible views </h2>
<p>Nature is at the heart of Hotel Eiger and staying here will give you the opportunity to really appreciate the beauty Switzerland has to offer. All the bedrooms have balconies with spectacular views of the landscape, from the snowy peaks of the Eiger mountain and <a data-udi="umb://document/1a5883a1530346a9ab78607d76c2e656" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1a5883a1530346a9ab78607d76c2e656}" title="Jungfrau Ski Region">Jungfrau ski area</a> to the forest that surrounds the traditional resort of <a data-udi="umb://document/c494e0deab1140028dfcdd140d9451cc" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c494e0deab1140028dfcdd140d9451cc}" title="Murren">Mürren</a>. The sun terrace also provides fantastic views of the mountains for those of you with a forest view, so you can really experience it all.</p>
<h2>Food and drink</h2>
<p>Hotel Eiger is known for it's sophisticated cuisine and specially selected, regional ingredients used in its dishes. Enjoy a selection of pastries and mountain cheeses at breakfast, all with views of the peaks from the sun terrace. Have dinner in the cosy restaurant and experience some of Switzerland's finest gastronomy accompanied by a glass of wine. There'll also be opportunity for a cocktail or two in the evening at the <span>Tächi Bar where they also serve a selection of hot and soft drinks. </span></p>
<h2>Spa and wellness facilities </h2>
<p><span>The alpine wellness area at this hotel offers some fantastic facilities included with your stay. </span>Experience the <span>Eiger, Mönch and Jungfrau mountains from the comfort of the indoor heated swimming pool and jacuzzi. Relax in the sauna which also has a Kneipp pool or spoil yourself and have a soothing massage tailored to you in one of the hotel's treatment rooms. </span></p>
<h3>Why is this an Inghams' Choice property?</h3>
<p><strong>Family run hotel</strong> - Hotel Eiger is a charming, family run hotel and is a fantastic choice for families looking for a warm and welcoming stay. </p>
<p><strong>Swiss cuisine</strong> - The restaurant at Hotel Eiger has a reputation for it's regional dishes and is the perfect place if you want to try some local Swiss dishes.</p>
<p><strong>Sit back and relax</strong> - With some fantastic spa facilities, and some incredible views, Hotel Eiger is the best choice if you want somewhere you can truly relax after a day on the slopes. </p>]]></description>
