  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Forest Side Twins</strong> are around 22<span>m² sleeping up to three people. Located at the side of the hotel, these rooms are quieter and overlook the forest.</span></p>
<p><strong>Mountain View Twins</strong> are around 20<span>m² sleeping two people, these rooms have a balcony with mountain views of the Eiger, Mönch and Jungfrau.</span></p>
<p><strong>Mountain View Triple</strong> <strong>Rooms</strong> are around 20<span>m²  sleeping three people and have a balcony. These rooms are on request so please call us to book.</span></p>
<p><strong>One Bedroom</strong> <strong>Suites </strong>are spacious at around 50<span>m² sleeping up to four, and have a south facing balcony. These rooms have a shower room. These rooms are also on request, so please call us to book.</span></p>
<p><strong>Single</strong> <strong>Rooms</strong> are around 15-17m² sleeping one. Rooms with forest or mountain views are available. These rooms are on request so please call us to book.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Bedroom facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Satellite TV</li>
<li>Radio</li>
<li>Telephone</li>
<li>Mini bar</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Hairdryer </li>
<li>Bath or shower </li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
